Package: libhadoop 
Authors: Arun C Murthy <arunc@yahoo-inc.com> 

MOTIVATION

The libhadoop package contains the native code for any of hadoop (http://lucene.apache.org/hadoop). 

IMPROVEMENTS

Any suggestions for improvements or patched should be sent to hadoop-dev@lucene.apache.org. Please go through http://wiki.apache.org/lucene-hadoop/HowToContribute for more information on how to contribute.
